| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3140 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a4ffa93f-d4d9-571c-9aa7-5ccfd92748e4"
